title: Google pitches media outlets on AI that could help produce news

title: Poll: Returning to the moon a low priority to Americans

title: Kevin Mitnick, hacker and fugitive turned security consultant, dies at 59
description: Kevin Mitnick, whose cyber crimes inspired the 2000 film "Take Down" and who was the subject of a highly publicized FBI manhunt, died of pancreatic cancer.
